flowchart TD
    A[Start VolumeScaler Operator]
    B[Initialize Kubernetes Clients & Event Recorder]
    C[Load Kubernetes Configuration - inClusterOrKubeconfig]
    D[Enter reconcileLoop]

    E[Fetch PVC Usage from Kubelet /stats/summary API via Node Proxy]
    F[List All VolumeScaler CRs]
    G[Match PVCs with VolumeScaler CRs]

    H[For Each Matched PVC]
    I[Parse VolumeScaler Spec - Threshold, Scale, ScaleType, MaxSize, CooldownPeriod]
    J[Recalculate Usage % Against PVC Spec Size]
    K[Cap Display Values - Usage at 100%, Used at Spec Size]
    L[Patch VolumeScaler Status with Current Usage]

    M{Has PVC Reached Max Size?}
    N{Is a Resize In Progress?}
    O{Resize Completed?}
    P{In Cooldown Period?}
    Q{Usage >= Threshold?}

    R[Compute New Size - Fixed or Percentage]
    S[Cap New Size at MaxSize if Needed]
    T[Patch PVC Spec to Request New Size]
    U[Update VolumeScaler Status - resizeInProgress, scaledAt, lastRequestedSize, reachedMaxSize]

    V[Emit Events for Each Significant Action or Error]
    W[Sleep for 60 Seconds]
    X[Repeat reconcileLoop]

    %% Flow connections
    A --> B
    B --> C
    C --> D
    D --> E
    E --> F
    F --> G
    G --> H
    H --> I
    I --> J
    J --> K
    K --> L
    L --> M

    M -- Yes --> V
    M -- No --> N
    N -- Yes --> O
    O -- Completed --> U
    O -- Still In Progress --> V
    N -- No --> Q
    Q -- Yes --> P
    P -- In Cooldown --> V
    P -- OK to Scale --> R
    R --> S
    S --> T
    T --> U
    U --> V
    Q -- No --> V

    V --> W
    W --> X
    X --> D
